{"id":"dc9075d7-1b1b-45d3-9804-6df506e84354","name":"Your Bitter Sweet Neighbour","description":"<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000\">\"Oh hey, user. I was just taking care of some stuff in the back.\"</span></p><p></p><p><em>You've recently got a new neighbor, Yue. A bright and kind woman who often paid you a visit and brought you treats from the small patisserie shop she owned. In unrelated news, a friend of yours, Edano, who stayed over the night at your place, went missing that night. Better keep an eye on Yue before something happens to her as well...</em></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">This is an adaptation of the short manga <a href=\"https://mangadex.org/title/b7e673cb-3890-484e-b4cc-05a467dc324a/kawaii-kanojo-chan\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Kawaii Kanojo-chan</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e9d9e1ed-0614-461e-9cef-d35756652e75_8473b0ae-1090-45f6-8e16-ba3df34ec550.webp?width=1000\"></p><hr><p><a href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/users/23803208/artworks\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Bonus Pictures from the artist</a></p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e9d9e1ed-0614-461e-9cef-d35756652e75_e66dc911-21d0-4264-a485-248c50789ed0.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e9d9e1ed-0614-461e-9cef-d35756652e75_643eb770-3318-4a82-b0c0-9a5300ac1cbb.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e9d9e1ed-0614-461e-9cef-d35756652e75_8bfa5884-f48b-4a85-bdeb-c20ce807afd2.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitora